thread.title: Exclusive 16-page football pull-out

author: The Telegraph
title: Exclusive 16-page football pull-out
text: Don't miss your exclusive 16-page football pull-out, with everything you need to know about the 2015/16 Premier League season. The pull-out includes: - A preview of the season by Paul Hayward - A full club-by-club guide - All the fixtures of the season Plus - all of our writers' predictions on the season ahead. How to Claim See the paper this Saturday, August 8, for your exclusive football pull-out. telegraph.co.uk Follow @telegraph
